textContent:
---happy birthmonth bby---

Happy birthmonth my bbycakes! I'm so excited to spend your birthday together for the first time!!! I'm really thankful that I'll get to spend your special day with you!

---away tayo ih---

Nag away tayo earlier this week and wala lang HUHUHU. I just want to reaffirm and reassure you na I'll never ever give up on you, na I'll always try to be a better person for you, that I'll always love you, and that I'll always put in the work and effort to keep loving you!! Kaya wag mo ko iiwan and susukuan ah? Iiyak ako huhuhu. ABABABAYU DIDIW BBY!!!

---anxiety---

Medyo nakakaanxious yung situation ko sa work now and hopefully by the time you're reading this may work parin ako HAHAHAHA. Things are looking good naman based sa mga sinasabi ni ivan, and I'm trying my best to be optimistic. Pero i just cant help but feel anxious bby and I just want to thank you kase amdyan ka lage for me. You make me feel at peace and calm. I love it so much when you're by my side and i want it to stay that way forever. Hug tight bby mwaaa.
